text: Your Highness is a 2011 fantasy-comedy movie produced by Scott Stuber, Jon Mone, Danny McBride, Mark Huffam and Andrew Z. Davis, and directed by David Gordon Green. It was released on April 8, 2011 in North America. The movie received negative reviews with Rotten Tomatoes giving it a 26% and Metacritic gave it a 31 out of 100. == Cast == *Danny McBride as Thadeous *James Franco as Fabious *Natalie Portman as Isabel *Zooey Deschanel as Belladonna *Justin Theroux as Leezar *Damian Lewis as Courtney *Toby Jones as Julie *Brian Steele *Charles Dance as The King and father of Thadeous and Fabious *Rasmus Hardiker as Courtney *Noah Huntley as Head Knight *Eva Wyrwal as Dwarf Queen *Amber Anderson as Maiden ==Other websites== *Your Highness' Official website * Category:2011 comedy movies Category:2011 fantasy movies Category:2010s American fantasy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:2010s English-language movies Category:Movies directed by David Gordon Green Category:Universal Pictures movies Category:Movies set in Belfast
